<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: orbital bombardment targeter -->
  <OrbitalTargeterBombardment.label>軌道轟炸導航器</OrbitalTargeterBombardment.label>
  <!-- EN: An ancient targeting apparatus for an orbital bombardment system. This unit designates a target and transmits the coordinates to a network of satellites, which then bombard the target area with kinetic impactors. This unit has been reprogrammed to accept unauthorized users, but once it is used, the network will detect the incursion and cut off the link permanently. -->
  <OrbitalTargeterBombardment.description>一種軌道轟炸系統的古老瞄準裝置。這個裝置會指定目標並將座標傳送到衛星網路，然後用動能衝擊器轟炸目標區域。本裝置已被破解為接受未經授權的使用者，一旦使用，衛星網路會偵測到入侵，永久切斷連線。</OrbitalTargeterBombardment.description>
  <!-- EN: charge -->
  <OrbitalTargeterBombardment.comps.CompReloadable.chargeNoun>充能</OrbitalTargeterBombardment.comps.CompReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <OrbitalTargeterBombardment.comps.CompReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷卻</OrbitalTargeterBombardment.comps.CompReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: orbital bombardment targeter -->
  <OrbitalTargeterBombardment.verbs.Verb_Bombardment.label>軌道轟炸導航器</OrbitalTargeterBombardment.verbs.Verb_Bombardment.label>
  
  <!-- EN: orbital power beam targeter -->
  <OrbitalTargeterPowerBeam.label>軌道光束導航器</OrbitalTargeterPowerBeam.label>
  <!-- EN: An ancient targeting unit for a network of power-collection satellites. Once aimed at a target, it directs ancient satellites to begin beaming power down in a massive column of electromagnetic energy. This power can safely be collected in a giant absorption dish. Since you have no absorption dish, you'll be aiming it at enemies, at which point the power column will turn the area into a thousand-degree inferno. This will last until the satellites detect the unsafe targeting, shut themselves down, and permanently deactivate the targeter. -->
  <OrbitalTargeterPowerBeam.description>一種網路衛星收集能量的古老瞄準裝置。一旦瞄準目標，它會指示古老衛星開始聚集能量，向下發射一道光柱。光柱可以安全地收集在巨大天線盤中。由於你沒有天線盤，那就把它瞄準敵人。此時，光柱就會將該區域變成地獄火海。這將持續到衛星偵測到不安全的目標，才會自行關閉、永久停用導航器。</OrbitalTargeterPowerBeam.description>
  <!-- EN: charge -->
  <OrbitalTargeterPowerBeam.comps.CompReloadable.chargeNoun>充能</OrbitalTargeterPowerBeam.comps.CompReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <OrbitalTargeterPowerBeam.comps.CompReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷卻</OrbitalTargeterPowerBeam.comps.CompReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: orbital power beam targeter -->
  <OrbitalTargeterPowerBeam.verbs.Verb_PowerBeam.label>軌道光束導航器</OrbitalTargeterPowerBeam.verbs.Verb_PowerBeam.label>
  
  <!-- EN: tornado generator -->
  <TornadoGenerator.label>龍捲風產生器</TornadoGenerator.label>
  <!-- EN: An ancient control unit for a network of weather-control satellites. This device has had certain failsafes bypassed; it is capable of causing a massive air current disturbance, which will generate a tornado at a chosen location. The weather network will detect this unauthorized intrusion and lock out the device after use, but the tornado will be left to spend its energy normally. -->
  <TornadoGenerator.description>一種網路衛星控制天候的古老控制裝置。此裝置能夠避免不安定因素；它能夠引起大規模的氣流干擾，在指定的位置產生龍捲風。網路衛星偵測到這種未經授權的入侵使用，就會被鎖定，龍捲風也會隨著時間逐漸消失。</TornadoGenerator.description>
